UMENGAMELI waseZimbabwe omusha, uMnuz Emmerson Mnangagwa unxuse ukuthi kube nobumbano kubantu basezweni lakhe izolo. UMnangagwa ukusho lokhu ngemuva kokuba kube nezinsolo zokuthi kube nobukhoshosho ngokunqoba kwakhe ukhetho. Uthe abantu baseZimbabwe kumele bakuthathe njengokunqoba ukuthi bakwazi ukuvota ngokukhululeka ngemuva kweminyaka eminingi bengaphansi kwengcindezelo kaMnuz Robert Mugabe obe ngumengameli wakhona isikhathi eside engashintshwa. Ngakolunye uhlangothi umholi weqembu eliphikisayo kuleli lizwe uMnuz Nelson Chamisa weMDC Alliance, uthe akayikholwa indaba yalama voti ngoba vele uMnangagwa wayengumngani kaMugabe owayephethe ngesandla sensimbi eZimbabwe. Ekhuluma kwabezindaba uMnangagwa uthe: “Izwe libonile ukuthi ukhetho belukhululekile futhi konke kuhambe ngendlela.”